{"route":"/docs/reference/model/bibliography/","title":"Bibliography","description":"Documentation for the `bibliography` function.","part":null,"outline":[{"id":"summary","name":"概要","children":[]},{"id":"スタイル","name":"スタイル","children":[]},{"id":"例","name":"例","children":[]},{"id":"parameters","name":"引数","children":[{"id":"parameters-sources","name":"sources","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-title","name":"title","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-full","name":"full","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-style","name":"style","children":[]}]}],"body":{"kind":"func","content":{"path":[],"name":"bibliography","title":"Bibliography","keywords":[],"oneliner":"参考文献 / 引用文献リスト。","element":true,"contextual":false,"deprecation":null,"details":"<p>参考文献 / 引用文献リスト。</p>\n<p>次の2つの形式のどちらかの参考文献ファイルへのパスを指定してこの関数を呼び出すと、新しい引用文献リストを作成できます。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hayagriva <code>.yml</code> ファイル。\nHayagrivaはTypstで使用するためにデザインされた新しい書誌ファイルフォーマットです。\n詳しくは<a href=\"https://github.com/typst/hayagriva/blob/main/docs/file-format.md\">ドキュメント</a>をご覧ください。</li>\n<li>BibLaTeX <code>.bib</code> ファイル。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>文書内に参考文献を追加すると、参照構文（<code><span class=\"typ-ref\">@key</span></code>）や引用関数の明示的な呼び出し（<code><span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">cite</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-label\">&lt;key&gt;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span></code>）を使って<a href=\"/docs/reference/model/cite/\">引用</a>を始めることができます。\n参考文献リストには、文書内で参照された作品の文献だけが表示されます。</p>\n<h2 id=\"スタイル\">スタイル</h2>\n<p>Typstは、内蔵の<a href=\"/docs/reference/model/bibliography/#parameters-style\">引用と文献スタイル</a>を幅広く取り揃えています。\nさらに、独自の<a href=\"https://citationstyles.org/\">CSL</a>（Citation Style Language）ファイルを追加して使用することもできます。\nどのスタイルを使えばいいか迷う方のために、分野ごとによく使われるスタイルを以下の表にまとめています。</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>分野</th><th>Typical Styles</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>工学、IT</td><td><code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;ieee&quot;</span></code></td></tr>\n<tr><td>心理学、ライフサイエンス</td><td><code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;apa&quot;</span></code></td></tr>\n<tr><td>社会科学</td><td><code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;chicago-author-date&quot;</span></code></td></tr>\n<tr><td>人文学</td><td><code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;mla&quot;</span></code>, <code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;chicago-notes&quot;</span></code>, <code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;harvard-cite-them-right&quot;</span></code></td></tr>\n<tr><td>経済学</td><td><code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;harvard-cite-them-right&quot;</span></code></td></tr>\n<tr><td>物理学</td><td><code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;american-physics-society&quot;</span></code></td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"例\">例</h2>\n<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code>This was already noted by\npirates long ago. <span class=\"typ-ref\">@arrgh</span>\n\nMultiple sources say <span class=\"typ-escape\">...</span>\n<span class=\"typ-ref\">@arrgh</span> <span class=\"typ-ref\">@netwok</span>.\n\n<span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">bibliography</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;works.bib&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/209df19e613387ac8475d78ce387afdf.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>","example":null,"self":false,"params":[{"name":"sources","details":"<p>1つまたは複数のHayagriva<code>.yml</code>やBibLaTeX<code>.bib</code>ファイルへのパスや生バイト。</p>\n<p>以下の形式で指定できます。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>読み込む参考文献ファイルのパス。\nパスに関する詳細は<a href=\"/docs/reference/syntax/#paths\">パスの章</a>をご参照ください。</li>\n<li>参考文献情報がデコードできる生バイト。</li>\n<li>上記を要素とする配列。</li>\n</ul>","example":null,"types":["str","bytes","array"],"strings":[],"default":null,"positional":true,"named":false,"required":true,"variadic":false,"settable":false},{"name":"title","details":"<p>参考文献のタイトル。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code><span class=\"typ-key\">auto</span></code>に設定すると、<a href=\"/docs/reference/text/text/#parameters-lang\">テキストの言語</a>に適したタイトルが表示されます。これがデフォルトです。</li>\n<li><code><span class=\"typ-key\">none</span></code>に設定すると、参考文献のタイトルは何も表示されません。</li>\n<li>独自のタイトルはコンテンツで渡します。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>参考文献の見出しはデフォルトでは番号が振られませんが、show-setルールで強制的に見出し番号をつけることも可能です。\n<code><span class=\"typ-key\">show</span> <span class=\"typ-func\">bibliography</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-key\">set</span> <span class=\"typ-func\">heading</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>numbering<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;1.&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span></code></p>","example":null,"types":["none","auto","content"],"strings":[],"default":"<code><span class=\"typ-key\">auto</span></code>","positional":false,"named":true,"required":false,"variadic":false,"settable":true},{"name":"full","details":"<p>文書内で引用されていないものも含めて、参考文献ファイルにある全ての文献を出力するかどうか。</p>\n<p>個々の引用文献を表示させずに追加するには、 <a href=\"/docs/reference/model/cite/#parameters-form\"><code>form</code></a> を <code><span class=\"typ-key\">none</span></code>として <a href=\"/docs/reference/model/cite/\"><code>cite</code></a> 関数を使用します。</p>","example":null,"types":["bool"],"strings":[],"default":"<code><span class=\"typ-key\">false</span></code>","positional":false,"named":true,"required":false,"variadic":false,"settable":true},{"name":"style","details":"<p>参考文献スタイル。</p>\n<p>以下のいずれかの方法で指定します。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>組み込みスタイル（下記参照）のいずれかの名前を持つ文字列。\n以下に挙げるスタイルのいくつかは、フルネームと短いエイリアスの2回表示されています。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://citationstyles.org/\">CSL ファイル</a>へのパスを示す文字列。\nパスに関する詳細は<a href=\"/docs/reference/syntax/#paths\">Pathセクション</a>を参照してください。</li>\n<li>CSLスタイルがデコードされるべき生バイト。</li>\n</ul>","example":null,"types":["str","bytes"],"strings":[{"string":"alphanumeric","details":"<p>Alphanumeric</p>"},{"string":"american-anthropological-association","details":"<p>American Anthropological Association</p>"},{"string":"american-chemical-society","details":"<p>American Chemical Society</p>"},{"string":"american-geophysical-union","details":"<p>American Geophysical Union</p>"},{"string":"american-institute-of-aeronautics-and-astronautics","details":"<p>American Institute of Aeronautics and Astronautics</p>"},{"string":"american-institute-of-physics","details":"<p>American Institute of Physics 4th edition</p>"},{"string":"american-medical-association","details":"<p>American Medical Association 11th edition</p>"},{"string":"american-meteorological-society","details":"<p>American Meteorological Society</p>"},{"string":"american-physics-society","details":"<p>American Physical Society</p>"},{"string":"american-physiological-society","details":"<p>American Physiological Society</p>"},{"string":"american-political-science-association","details":"<p>American Political Science Association</p>"},{"string":"american-psychological-association","details":"<p>American Psychological Association 7th edition</p>"},{"string":"american-society-for-microbiology","details":"<p>American Society for Microbiology</p>"},{"string":"american-society-of-civil-engineers","details":"<p>American Society of Civil Engineers</p>"},{"string":"american-society-of-mechanical-engineers","details":"<p>American Society of Mechanical Engineers</p>"},{"string":"american-sociological-association","details":"<p>American Sociological Association 6th/7th edition</p>"},{"string":"angewandte-chemie","details":"<p>Angewandte Chemie International Edition</p>"},{"string":"annual-reviews","details":"<p>Annual Reviews (sorted by order of appearance)</p>"},{"string":"annual-reviews-author-date","details":"<p>Annual Reviews (author-date)</p>"},{"string":"associacao-brasileira-de-normas-tecnicas","details":"<p>Associação Brasileira de Normas Técnicas (Português - Brasil)</p>"},{"string":"association-for-computing-machinery","details":"<p>Association for Computing Machinery</p>"},{"string":"biomed-central","details":"<p>BioMed Central</p>"},{"string":"bristol-university-press","details":"<p>Bristol University Press</p>"},{"string":"british-medical-journal","details":"<p>BMJ</p>"},{"string":"cell","details":"<p>Cell</p>"},{"string":"chicago-author-date","